[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">spoke</st> about <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"01945 0413\">Sure to be judged is</st> <st data-num=\"05015\" class=\"\">Nebo</st>! <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> it will be <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07156\" class=\"\">Kiriathaim</st><n id=\"4\" /> will <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">suffer disgrace</st>. It will be <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">captured</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Its <st data-num=\"04869\" class=\"\">fortress</st><n id=\"5\" /> will <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">suffer disgrace</st>. It will be <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">torn down</st>!<n id=\"6\" /></p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">People will <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08416\" class=\"\">praise</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">anymore</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The enemy will capture <st data-num=\"02809\" class=\"\">Heshbon</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">plot</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"07451 05921\">how to destroy</st> Moab,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">saying, \u2018<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Come</st>, let\u2019s <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">put an end</st> to that <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st>!\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">City of <st data-num=\"04086\" class=\"\">Madmen</st>, you will <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> be <st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">destructive army</st> will <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">march</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">against</st> you.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">Cries</st> of <st data-num=\"06818\" class=\"\">anguish</st> will arise in <st data-num=\"02773\" class=\"\">Horonaim</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018Oh, the <st data-num=\"07701\" class=\"\">ruin</st> and <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st>!\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will be <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">crushed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"06810\" class=\"\">children</st> will <st data-num=\"08085 02201\">cry out in distress</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st> they will <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">climb</st> the <st data-num=\"04608\" class=\"\">slopes</st> of <st data-num=\"03872\" class=\"\">Luhith</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01065\" class=\"\">weeping</st> <st data-num=\"01065\" class=\"\">continually</st> as they go.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> on the <st data-num=\"04174\" class=\"\">road down</st> to <st data-num=\"02773\" class=\"\">Horonaim</st> <p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> the <st data-num=\"06818\" class=\"\">cries</st> of <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">distress</st> over the <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will hear, \u2018<st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">Run</st>! <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">Save</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">yourselves</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">even if you must <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> like a lonely <st data-num=\"06176\" class=\"\">shrub</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>!\u2019<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201cMoab, you <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trust</st> in the <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">things</st> you <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">do</st> and in your <st data-num=\"0214\" class=\"\">riches</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588 03282\">So</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">too</st> will be <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">conquered</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your god <st data-num=\"03645\" class=\"\">Chemosh</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">go</st> into <st data-num=\"01473\" class=\"\">exile</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">along with</st> his <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> and his <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyer</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">town</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">Not</st> one <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">town</st> will <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escape</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The towns in the <st data-num=\"06010\" class=\"\">valley</st> will be <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The cities on the <st data-num=\"04334\" class=\"\">high plain</st> will be <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">laid waste</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, have <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">spoken</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">Set up</st> a <st data-num=\"06725\" class=\"\">gravestone</st> for <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> it will <st data-num=\"05327\" class=\"\">certainly</st> be <st data-num=\"05327\" class=\"\">laid in ruins</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Its <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">laid waste</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0369 03427 02004\">become uninhabited</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"0779\" class=\"\">curse</st> on anyone who is <st data-num=\"07423\" class=\"\">lax</st> in <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"04399\" class=\"\">work</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"0779\" class=\"\">curse</st> on anyone who <st data-num=\"04513\" class=\"\">keeps</st> from <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">carrying out</st> his <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">destruction</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201cFrom its <st data-num=\"05271\" class=\"\">earliest days</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> has <st data-num=\"07599\" class=\"\">lived undisturbed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> been <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">taken</st> into <st data-num=\"01473\" class=\"\">exile</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">Its people</st> are like wine allowed to <st data-num=\"08252\" class=\"\">settle undisturbed</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> its <st data-num=\"08105\" class=\"\">dregs</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"07324\" class=\"\">poured out</st> from one <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">jar</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">another</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They are like wine that <st data-num=\"02940\" class=\"\">tastes</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">like it always did</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">whose <st data-num=\"07381\" class=\"\">aroma</st> has remained <st data-num=\"03808 04171\">unchanged</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651 02009\">But</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> is <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st> when I will <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06808\" class=\"\">men</st> against Moab who will <st data-num=\"06808\" class=\"\">empty</st> it <st data-num=\"06808\" class=\"\">out</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"07324\" class=\"\">empty</st> the <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">towns</st> of their people,<p class=\"poetry\">then will <st data-num=\"05310\" class=\"\">lay</st> those <st data-num=\"05035\" class=\"\">towns</st> <st data-num=\"05310\" class=\"\">in ruins</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The people of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will be <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">disappointed</st> by their god <st data-num=\"03645\" class=\"\">Chemosh</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will be as disappointed <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">were</st> <p class=\"poetry\">when they put their <st data-num=\"04009\" class=\"\">trust</st> in the calf god at <st data-num=\"01008\" class=\"\">Bethel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">How</st> can you men of Moab <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"0587\" class=\"\">We</st> are <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">heroes</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0582\" class=\"\">men</st> who are <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">mighty</st> in <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st>?\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will be <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>. Its <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> will be <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">invaded</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Its <st data-num=\"04005\" class=\"\">finest</st> <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st> will <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"02875\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0343\" class=\"\">destruction</st> is <st data-num=\"07138 0935\">at hand</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">Disaster</st> will <st data-num=\"04116 03966\">come on it quickly</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">Mourn</st> for that nation, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> you nations living <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">around</st> it,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> you nations that <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> of its <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">fame</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Mourn and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">Alas</st>, its <st data-num=\"05797\" class=\"\">powerful</st> <st data-num=\"04294\" class=\"\">influence</st> has been <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">broken</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Its <st data-num=\"08597\" class=\"\">glory</st> and <st data-num=\"04731\" class=\"\">power</st> have been done away with!\u2019<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">Come down</st> from your <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">place of honor</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sit</st> on the <st data-num=\"06772\" class=\"\">dry ground</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> you who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"01323 01769\">Dibon</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the one who will <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">attack</st> you;<p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> your <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortifications</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"06177\" class=\"\">Aroer</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stand</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">by</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">road</st> and <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watch</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">Question</st> the man who is <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">fleeing</st> and the woman who is <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escaping</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">Ask</st> them, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> has <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">happened</st>?\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will answer, <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">\u2018Moab</st> is <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">disgraced</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> it has <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">fallen</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">Wail</st> and <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cry out</st> in mourning!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">Announce</st> along the <st data-num=\"0769\" class=\"\">Arnon</st> River<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> has been <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">Judgment</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">cities</st> on the <st data-num=\"04334\" class=\"\">high plain</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"02473\" class=\"\">Holon</st>, <st data-num=\"03096\" class=\"\">Jahzah</st>, and <st data-num=\"04158\" class=\"\">Mephaath</st>; ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"01769\" class=\"\">Dibon</st>, <st data-num=\"05015\" class=\"\">Nebo</st>, and <st data-num=\"01015\" class=\"\">Beth Diblathaim</st>; ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"07156\" class=\"\">Kiriathaim</st>, <st data-num=\"01014\" class=\"\">Beth Gamul</st>, and <st data-num=\"01010\" class=\"\">Beth Meon</st>; ",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"07152\" class=\"\">Kerioth</st> and <st data-num=\"01224\" class=\"\">Bozrah</st>. It will come <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> of <st data-num=\"0776 04124\">Moab</st>, both <st data-num=\"07350\" class=\"\">far</st> and <st data-num=\"07138\" class=\"\">near</st>. ",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07161\" class=\"\">might</st> will be <st data-num=\"01438\" class=\"\">crushed</st>. Its <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">power</st> will be <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">broken</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> has <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">vaunted</st> itself <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">me</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">So</st> <st data-num=\"07937\" class=\"\">make</st> him <st data-num=\"07937\" class=\"\">drunk</st> with the wine of my wrath<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">until he <st data-num=\"05606\" class=\"\">splashes</st><n id=\"2\" /> around in his own <st data-num=\"06892\" class=\"\">vomit</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">until others <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">treat</st> <st data-num=\"01571 01931\">him</st> as a <st data-num=\"07814\" class=\"\">laughingstock</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">For <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> you people of Moab <st data-num=\"07814 01961\">laugh at</st> the people of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Did</st> you think that they <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">were</st> nothing but <st data-num=\"01590\" class=\"\">thieves</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">shook</st> your <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">head in contempt</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">every time</st> you <st data-num=\"01696\">talked</st> about them?<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">Leave</st> your <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st>, you <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st> of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Go and <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">live</st> in the <st data-num=\"05553\" class=\"\">cliffs</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Be</st> like a <st data-num=\"03123\" class=\"\">dove</st> that <st data-num=\"07077\" class=\"\">makes</st> its <st data-num=\"07077\" class=\"\">nest</st><p class=\"poetry\">high <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">sides</st> of a <st data-num=\"06310 06354\">ravine</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> how <st data-num=\"01347\" class=\"\">proud</st> the people of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> are,<p class=\"poetry\">I know <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">how</st> <st data-num=\"01343\" class=\"\">haughty</st> they are.<p class=\"poetry\">I have heard how <st data-num=\"01363\" class=\"\">arrogant</st>, <st data-num=\"01347\" class=\"\">proud</st>, and <st data-num=\"01346\" class=\"\">haughty</st> they <st data-num=\"01363 01347 01346\">are</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">what a <st data-num=\"07312\" class=\"\">high opinion</st> they have <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">of themselves</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> that<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> how <st data-num=\"05678\" class=\"\">arrogant</st> they are.<p class=\"poetry\">But their pride is <st data-num=\"03808 03651\">ill founded</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"0907\" class=\"\">boastings</st> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">prove to be</st> <st data-num=\"03808 03651\">false</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">So</st> I will <st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">weep with sorrow</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cry out</st> in sadness for <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01897\" class=\"\">moan</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"07025\" class=\"\">Kir Heres</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">weep</st> for the <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">grapevines</st> of <st data-num=\"07643\" class=\"\">Sibmah</st><p class=\"poetry\">just like the town of <st data-num=\"03270\" class=\"\">Jazer</st> <st data-num=\"01065\" class=\"\">weeps</st> over them.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"05189\" class=\"\">branches</st> once <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">spread</st> as far as the Dead <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">Sea</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05060\" class=\"\">reached</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">as far as</st> the town of <st data-num=\"03270\" class=\"\">Jazer</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyer</st> will <st data-num=\"05921 05307\">ravage</st> <p class=\"poetry\">her <st data-num=\"07019\" class=\"\">fig, date</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"01210\" class=\"\">grape crops</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">Joy</st> and <st data-num=\"01524\" class=\"\">gladness</st> will <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">disappear</st><p class=\"poetry\">from the <st data-num=\"03759\" class=\"\">fruitful</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07673\" class=\"\">stop</st> the flow of <st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">wine</st> from the <st data-num=\"03342\" class=\"\">winepresses</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> one will <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">stomp</st> on the grapes there and <st data-num=\"01959\" class=\"\">shout for joy</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"01959\" class=\"\">shouts</st> there will be shouts of soldiers,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> the <st data-num=\"01959\" class=\"\">shouts</st> of those making wine.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02201\" class=\"\">Cries of anguish</st> raised from <st data-num=\"02809\" class=\"\">Heshbon</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"0500\" class=\"\">Elealeh</st><p class=\"poetry\">will be sounded <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">as far as</st> <st data-num=\"03096\" class=\"\">Jahaz</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sounded</st> from <st data-num=\"06820\" class=\"\">Zoar</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">as far as</st> <st data-num=\"02773\" class=\"\">Horonaim</st> and <st data-num=\"05697\" class=\"\">Eglath</st> <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">Shelishiyah</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">even</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">waters</st> of <st data-num=\"05249\" class=\"\">Nimrim</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"04923\" class=\"\">dried up</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07673\" class=\"\">put an end</st> in <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st><p class=\"poetry\">to those who <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">make offerings</st> at her <st data-num=\"01116\" class=\"\">places of worship</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will put an end to those who <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> to other <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "35"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">So</st> my <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st> <st data-num=\"01993\" class=\"\">moans</st> for <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st><p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"02485\" class=\"\">flute</st> playing a funeral song.<p class=\"poetry\">Yes, like a <st data-num=\"02485\" class=\"\">flute</st> playing a funeral song,<p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st> <st data-num=\"01993\" class=\"\">moans</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"07025\" class=\"\">Kir Heres</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"03502\" class=\"\">wealth</st> they have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">gained</st> will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">perish</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "36"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them will <st data-num=\"07144\" class=\"\">shave</st> their <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">heads</st> in mourning.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"01639\" class=\"\">cut off</st> their <st data-num=\"02206\" class=\"\">beards</st> to show their sorrow.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> make <st data-num=\"01417\" class=\"\">gashes</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> their <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"05921 04975\">put on</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "37"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">On</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01406\" class=\"\">housetops</st> in <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st><p class=\"poetry\">and in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> its <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">public squares</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">there will be nothing but <st data-num=\"04553\" class=\"\">mourning</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I will <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">break</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> like an <st data-num=\"0369 02656\">unwanted</st> <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">jar</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "38"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Oh, <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">how</st> <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">shattered</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will be! <p class=\"poetry\">Oh, how her people will <st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">wail</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Oh, <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">how</st> she will <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">turn</st> <st data-num=\"06203\" class=\"\">away</st><n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">shame</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> an <st data-num=\"07814\" class=\"\">object of ridicule</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"04288\" class=\"\">terrifying sight</st> to <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the nations that <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">surround</st> her.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "39"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>! Like an <st data-num=\"05404\" class=\"\">eagle</st> with <st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">outspread</st> <st data-num=\"03671\" class=\"\">wings</st><p class=\"poetry\">a nation will <st data-num=\"01675\" class=\"\">swoop down</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "40"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"07151\" class=\"\">towns</st><n id=\"1\" /> will be <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">captured</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">her <st data-num=\"04679\" class=\"\">fortresses</st> will be <st data-num=\"08610\" class=\"\">taken</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> the <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">frightened</st> <p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"03820 0802\">woman</st> in <st data-num=\"06887\" class=\"\">labor</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "41"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> will be <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> and no longer be a <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">nation</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> she has <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">vaunted</st> herself <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "42"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06343\" class=\"\">Terror</st>, <st data-num=\"06354\" class=\"\">pits</st>, and <st data-num=\"06341\" class=\"\">traps</st><n id=\"1\" /> are in store<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> the people who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "43"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Anyone who <st data-num=\"05211\" class=\"\">flees</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">at the sound of</st> <st data-num=\"06343\" class=\"\">terror</st><p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> a <st data-num=\"06354\" class=\"\">pit</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Anyone who <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">climbs</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">out of</st> the <st data-num=\"06354\" class=\"\">pit</st><p class=\"poetry\">will be <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">caught</st> in a <st data-num=\"06341\" class=\"\">trap</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">time</st> <st data-num=\"0935 0413\">is coming</st><p class=\"poetry\">when I will <st data-num=\"0413 06486\">punish</st> the people of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "44"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">In the <st data-num=\"06738\" class=\"\">shadows</st> of the walls of <st data-num=\"02809\" class=\"\">Heshbon</st><p class=\"poetry\">those trying to <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">escape</st> will <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stand</st> <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">helpless</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> a <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> will <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">burst forth</st> from <st data-num=\"02809\" class=\"\">Heshbon</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03852\" class=\"\">Flames</st> will shoot out <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">from</st> the former territory of <st data-num=\"05511\" class=\"\">Sihon</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">burn</st> the <st data-num=\"06285\" class=\"\">foreheads</st> of the people of <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06936\" class=\"\">skulls</st> of those <st data-num=\"07588\" class=\"\">war-loving</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">people</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "45"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st>, you are <st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">doomed</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> who worship <st data-num=\"03645\" class=\"\">Chemosh</st> will be <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> will be <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken away</st> <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">captive</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st> will be carried away into <st data-num=\"07633\" class=\"\">exile</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "46"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Yet in <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">future</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">reverse</st> <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab\u2019s</st> ill <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">fortune</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judgment</st> against <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moab</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">ends</st> <st data-num=\"02008\" class=\"\">here</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "47"
  }
]